664 A.2d 1352 James WINNING, III and Hilda Winning, his wife, and Brent Winning v. AETNA CASUALTY & SURETY COMPANY, Appellant. Supreme Court of Pennsylvania. Argued Sept. 19, 1995. Decided Oct. 11, 1995. *617Timothy J. Burdette and Bryan J. Smith, Pittsburgh, for Aetna. William M. Radcliffe, Uniontown, for Winning.

Before NIX, C.J., and FLAHERTY, ZAPPALA, CAPPY, CASTILLE and MONTEMURO, JJ.

ORDER

PER CURIAM:

Appeal dismissed as having been improvidently granted.

MONTEMURO, J., is sitting by designation.
